OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with bright and
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Remaining dry through
OL,7,Fthe afternoon with some sunny spells
OL,8,Fbut generally turning cloudier. A few
OL,9,Fspots of rain are possible over
OL,10,Fwestern Argyll, where it will also be
OL,11,Fwindy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome clear spells at first
OL,14,Fthis evening but soon turning cloudier
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,16,Fnorthwards. Cloudy overnight with
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
