OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain. Becoming drier with
OL,7,Fsunny spells for a time in the
OL,8,Fafternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,11,Fcloudy with showers and at times
OL,12,Flonger spells of heavier, more
OL,13,Fpersistent rain, though still with
OL,14,Fsome dry and bright spells. Winds
OL,15,Fstrengthening Tuesday, staying strong
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
